      <title>Netwerk24 称南非仍拥有高浓缩铀</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/south-africa-still-owns-highly-enriched-uranium-netwerk24-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Netwerk24 援引能源部长格韦德·曼塔谢的话报道，南非仍然拥有大量高浓缩铀。]]></description>
