    <item>
      <title>菲律宾加强南海前哨基地防御，将持续十年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/philippines-fortifies-south-china-sea-outpost-to-last-a-decade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据四位知情人士透露，菲律宾已对在有争议的南海搁浅的一艘二战时期的舰船进行了大规模增援，增援程度足以使这艘与北京关系紧张的前哨基地至少再维持十年。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/philippines-fortifies-south-china-sea-outpost-to-last-a-decade</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 06:20:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其因哈马斯“审查”争端封锁 Instagram</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/turkey-blocks-instagram-claims-hamas-condolences-censored</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在土耳其总统雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安的一名高级助手批评社交媒体平台“审查”与哈马斯政治领袖伊斯梅尔·哈尼亚之死相关的帖子后，土耳其互联网监管机构封锁了 Instagram 的访问。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/turkey-blocks-instagram-claims-hamas-condolences-censored</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 05:09:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台湾称澳门“一个中国”要求阻碍特使签证</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/macau-denies-entry-to-taiwan-official-in-one-china-spat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾称，派员工前往澳门代表处遇到困难，因为澳门特别行政区政府要求他们签署“一个中国原则”承诺才能获得签证。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/macau-denies-entry-to-taiwan-official-in-one-china-spat</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 03:23:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
