    <item>
      <title>泰国反对党领袖警告法院裁决前局势不稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/ahead-of-thai-court-rulings-reformist-sees-political-inferno</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国法院正准备裁决是否解散反对党以及是否应罢免总理，一位重要的反对党政治家表示，泰国面临再次陷入动荡的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/ahead-of-thai-court-rulings-reformist-sees-political-inferno</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 01:09:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>空军称变速箱导致日本“鱼鹰”飞机坠毁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/gearbox-caused-fatal-osprey-crash-in-japan-us-air-force-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国空军称，去年，一架美国军用“鱼鹰”飞机在日本沿海坠毁，因变速箱严重故障，造成 8 名飞行员死亡，这一原因与之前倾转旋翼机发生的一些事故类似。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/gearbox-caused-fatal-osprey-crash-in-japan-us-air-force-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 00:58:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>金正恩亲身参与朝鲜洪灾宣传活动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/kim-jong-un-wades-into-north-korean-floods-in-hands-on-propaganda-drive</link>
      <description><![CDATA[朝鲜领导人金正恩双脚踩在泥泞中，乘坐狭窄的橡皮救援船在汹涌的河面上救援，并指挥军用直升机在雨水浸湿的跑道上卸下撤离人员。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/kim-jong-un-wades-into-north-korean-floods-in-hands-on-propaganda-drive</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 21:00:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯囚犯交换后，包括《华尔街日报》记者在内的美国人抵达美国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/russia-releases-us-reporter-in-major-swap-for-kremlin-agents</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统乔·拜登和副总统卡玛拉·哈里斯欢迎《华尔街日报》记者埃文·格什科维奇、前美国海军陆战队员保罗·惠兰和其他获释的美国人回国，这是自冷战以来与俄罗斯最大规模的囚犯交换计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/russia-releases-us-reporter-in-major-swap-for-kremlin-agents</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 15:39:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登向内塔尼亚胡承诺“新的美国防御性军事部署”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/iran-buries-killed-hamas-official-as-israel-braces-for-revenge-attacks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在以色列面临报复暗杀哈马斯和真主党领导人的新威胁之际，总统乔·拜登向本杰明·内塔尼亚胡承诺“新的美国防御性军事部署”，但他也敦促以色列领导人推进停火努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/iran-buries-killed-hamas-official-as-israel-braces-for-revenge-attacks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 10:19:44 GMT</pubDate>
